"The CycloneDX tool is available in the ``conan.tools.sbom.cyclonedx`` "
"module. It provides the ``cyclonedx_1_4`` function which receives a "
"``conanfile`` and returns a dictionary with the SBOM data in the CycloneDX "
"1.4 JSON format."
